  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK878">
<l>vakaiyaṟintu taṟceytu taṟkāppa māyum </l>
<l>pakaivarkaṭ paṭṭa cerukku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The joy of one's foes will be destroyed if one guards oneself by knowing the way (of acting) and securing assistance.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
